Florida Marlins Last Year's Ranking: 21 Why They Might Be Better Than This: With Cameron Maybin, Michael Stanton, and Matt Dominguez , the organization has three five-star position prospects, and many believe that Logan Morrison should be the fourth; Kyle Skipworth is unfairly downgraded by a tough pro debut; left-handed behemoth Sean West is a favorite sleeper among scouts.
